text: Emphytoecia camousseighti is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Cerda in 1995. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Emphytoecia camousseighti. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1995
